{"tid":948430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【分享捐錢收據　善心人反被批做Show︰博咩？】","createTime":"2018-12-20T05:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T05:41:40.000Z","uid":225464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"16e325ec7a7b0a04274d00106e34620ba2dee645","tid":948430,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:15:36.000Z","msg":"捐錢呃LIKE又點<br />\n起碼人地真係捐咗錢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181220/bkn-20181220124355079-1220_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181220%2Fbkn-20181220124355079-1220_00822_001.html&d=0hdNa2H5pSPava9H49v2gNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=40bd3367\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181220/bkn-20181220124355079-1220_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zrfK5Nk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrfK5Nk.jpg&h=90436e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>分享捐錢收據　善心人反被批做Show︰博咩？</strong><br />\n<br />\n所謂「施比受更有福」，做善事除了幫到人，自己亦會快樂。不過有網民捐錢後在Facebook群組「巴打絲打Facebook Club」分享喜悅，竟反招來眾人批評。<br />\n<br />\n從事主上載的便利店收據可見，星期四（20日）凌晨4時許，他在天水圍一間便利店，向兒童癌病基金捐款5000港元。他直言︰「捐吓錢，人都開心啲，大家出一分力，幫吓有需要嘅人」。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到他的舉動卻引來網民反感，直指其「偽善」、「做善事Show off（炫耀），想博咩」、「咁少就唔好放上網」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有網民則大讚是好人好事︰「做善事會傳染㗎」、「可以鼓勵更多人去做善事」、「動機係乜都好，起碼真係幫到人呀」。<br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇呢？"},{"pid":"11f21f1e39480bc7ef746f2eff9b9d39e555ecbb","tid":948430,"uid":82532,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"捐錢呃LIKE又點<br />\n起碼人地真係捐咗錢<br />\n認同"},{"pid":"d6ac241e48e509a10b628724683e5485a57f5d12","tid":948430,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:19:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dccd6a2295f63377bc8f7dbe61c85092fe717e41","tid":948430,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"而家啲人真係好撚反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/